{
  "chapter": 14,
  "chapter_summary": "第十四回 患难情：高莫野在父亲高寿遭花门七毒行刺时挺身而出，却中了剧毒西域魔蓝。芮玮护送她前往小五台山求医，途中遭遇泰族人的迷烟陷阱。芮玮因吸入迷药昏倒，高莫野虽中毒虚弱，仍厉声喝止企图逃跑的御手，展现出患难中的坚韧与担当。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你站在那里做什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "你快去保护伯父！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_san_ye_shang_ren",
      "text": "你是死人吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_zhang_xian_zi",
      "text": "伯母快将伯父护到屋后，此地有我与野儿！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming_ci_ke",
      "text": "你们是什么人，胆敢将我父亲护卫杀伤？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_ci_ke",
      "speaker_name": "刺客",
      "listener": "char_gao_shou",
      "text": "不要走，留下命来！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nian_lao_ci_ke",
      "speaker_name": "年老刺客",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "你若要死得慢点，好好到一边去养息！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_nian_lao_ci_ke",
      "text": "你们可姓花？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nian_lao_ci_ke",
      "speaker_name": "年老刺客",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "咱们正是花门七毒！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_nian_lao_ci_ke",
      "text": "那七名护卫可是被你们的含沙射影杀伤？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nian_lao_ci_ke",
      "speaker_name": "年老刺客",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "姑娘既知道，就尝尝含沙射影滋味吧！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "小心他们的暗器，千万不要让他们接近！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "你……你……怎么啦？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你莫管我，快将三叶上人的人中穴用针刺一下。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_zhang_xian_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玉掌仙子",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "野儿……你……你……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_yu_zhang_xian_zi",
      "text": "娘不要急，外面尚有刺客，快拿一根针给大哥！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_san_ye_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "三叶上人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刚才发生什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_san_ye_shang_ren",
      "text": "上人快去吩咐卫士防卫四周，注意刺客，千万记住，教他们莫要与刺客正眼相视！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥，你将我抱到那五位身旁。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "这是怎么回事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_nian_lao_ci_ke",
      "text": "解药在哪里？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nian_lao_ci_ke",
      "speaker_name": "年老刺客",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "第三个瓶子可解她身上的毒气。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "好厉害的毒气，我只与他对了一掌便从皮肤中渗进，若非用内功逼住毒气，此刻早已死去！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "我扶你起来吧？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不行，我脚上的毒还没解，站不起来。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "我看可好了一点？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我用内功止也止不住啦！毒气仍一点一点上侵！",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shou",
      "speaker_name": "高寿",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这是西域魔蓝，我曾见过，中人一刻即死，快向那刺客索取解药，莫要迟了！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_nian_lao_ci_ke",
      "text": "快将解药取出，不要自讨苦吃！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nian_lao_ci_ke",
      "speaker_name": "年老刺客",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "那毒我也无法可解。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_zhang_xian_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玉掌仙子",
      "listener": "char_nian_lao_ci_ke",
      "text": "你快取出解药，要知你的兄弟也中了魔蓝毒！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nian_lao_ci_ke",
      "speaker_name": "年老刺客",
      "listener": "char_yu_zhang_xian_zi",
      "text": "就是我的兄弟，也无法可解！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_nian_lao_ci_ke",
      "text": "你胡说！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥逼他也没用，不如把他兄弟弄醒问他们较好。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "他们全死了……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nian_lao_ci_ke",
      "speaker_name": "年老刺客",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我的兄弟真中了魔蓝毒？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_zhang_xian_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玉掌仙子",
      "listener": "char_nian_lao_ci_ke",
      "text": "我们怎会骗你？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mian_xiong_ci_ke",
      "speaker_name": "面凶刺客",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我的兄弟真的死了，花门誓不与你们罢休！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_mian_xiong_ci_ke",
      "text": "我们无冤无仇，为何要取你兄弟的性命，这怪他们自讨，如今连野儿……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mian_xiong_ci_ke",
      "speaker_name": "面凶刺客",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你不要我兄弟的性命，就快将他们的毒血放尽，喂下最最滋补的药品，快！快！迟了不及。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "啊！我怎么没有想到他！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shou",
      "speaker_name": "高寿",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "此去小五台山要十日行程，野儿不能行走，只有劳动贤侄，耽误贤侄的时光……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_shou",
      "text": "别这样说，若非贤妹，我早已没命，此番无论任何艰难，都要尽力护送她到小五台山，请史不旧救她。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_zhang_xian_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玉掌仙子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "有你护送野儿去，我十分放心，现在时间宝贵，你们赶快动身吧！",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_gao_shou",
      "text": "爹，我走了以后要特别注意，莫要再被刺客闯进。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shou",
      "speaker_name": "高寿",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "我晓得，你快去吧，要知爹仅有你一个女儿，千万注意才是。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shou",
      "speaker_name": "高寿",
      "listener": "char_yu_zhang_xian_zi",
      "text": "这些刺客显系被奸人利用，剩下两个只要知道悔改，就放了他们吧！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "speaker_name": "高莫野",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥，怎么啦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_ye",
      "text": "你睡你的，我去看看。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_shou",
      "speaker_name": "御手",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "相公请看那群鬼画符野人，挡住去路！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_shou",
      "text": "怎么回事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_cai_se_luo_ren",
      "text": "让开路！让开路！……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hui_yi_lao_zhe",
      "text": "老丈，烦你叫他们让开路好吗？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_yi_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣老者",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "他们不会让开的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hui_yi_lao_zhe",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_yi_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣老者",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "他们族中一位青年人突生疾病躺在地上将要死去，依他们族里的风俗习惯，同伴要彩色哀号三天，那年青人的灵魂才能上升天国，否则暴毙不得超生，永沉地狱！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hui_yi_lao_zhe",
      "text": "他们是什么族人，讲的什么话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_yi_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣老者",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "他们是泰族人，讲的是泰语，敢情相公听不懂？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_shou",
      "text": "你可听说过泰族人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_shou",
      "speaker_name": "御手",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "怎没听过！这泰族人专门喜欢搞鬼画符的玩意，有一次……",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hui_yi_lao_zhe",
      "text": "那青年生的什么病？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_yi_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣老者",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "啊！从来没见过这种怪病，我与他们族人在路上走得好好的，突见横身一倒，在地上乱滚乱翻，惨声呼叫，越叫声音越小，那声音好不恐怖，现在已然叫不出声来，眼看就要断气，那样子实在可怜……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 14,
