      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hui_yi_lao_zhe",
      "text": "可否让我去看看那年青人？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_yi_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣老者",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "相公是医生吗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hui_yi_lao_zhe",
      "text": "你带我去看他，也许能治。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_yi_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣老者",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "他们说，相公若能治好青年人，全族感恩不尽，因那青年人是族长之子。",
